你能够调用以下的API:
[['CulturalMarketAnalysis.fetch_cultural_spending', {'name': 'CulturalMarketAnalysis.fetch_cultural_spending', 'description': 'This function retrieves cultural spending data during a specified crisis period.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'crisis_period', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The period of the crisis, e.g., 2008 for the financial crisis.'}, {'name': 'category', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The category of cultural spending, e.g., entertainment, arts.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'spending_data', 'description': 'A dataset of cultural spending during the crisis period.'}]}], ['CulturalMarketAnalysis.get_product_performance', {'name': 'CulturalMarketAnalysis.get_product_performance', 'description': 'This function retrieves the market performance of cultural products during a crisis period.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'crisis_period', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The period of the crisis, e.g., 2008 for the financial crisis.'}, {'name': 'product_types', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of product types to analyze, e.g., movies, music.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'performance_data', 'description': 'A dataset of product performance during the crisis period.'}]}], ['CulturalMarketAnalysis.study_graduates_spending', {'name': 'CulturalMarketAnalysis.study_graduates_spending', 'description': 'This function studies the spending habits of a specific demographic during a crisis period.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'crisis_period', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The period of the crisis, e.g., 2008 for the financial crisis.'}, {'name': 'demographic', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The demographic to study, e.g., recent_graduates.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'spending_habits', 'description': 'A dataset of spending habits for the specified demographic during the crisis period.'}]}], ['CulturalMarketAnalysis.fetch_innovation_trends', {'name': 'CulturalMarketAnalysis.fetch_innovation_trends', 'description': 'This function fetches future innovation trends in a cultural category from a specified source.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'source', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The source of the innovation trends, e.g., cultural_institute.'}, {'name': 'category', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The cultural category to analyze, e.g., entertainment.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'innovation_trends', 'description': 'A dataset of future innovation trends in the cultural category.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `CulturalMarketAnalysis.fetch_cultural_spending` 并传入 `crisis_period` 和 `category`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "CulturalMarketAnalysis.fetch_cultural_spending",
    "args": "{'crisis_period': '2008', 'category': 'entertainment'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
